  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Europe-wide awareness campaign to help prepare European citizens for the implementation of the UK’s new Immigration System from 1 January 2021</p>

  </div>
</div>

